query:
SELECT
                jobs.id,
                jobs.url,
                jobs.routing_key,
                jobs.details,
                COALESCE(
                    ARRAY_AGG(
                        JSON_BUILD_OBJECT(
                            'id', d.id,
                            'worker_name', d.worker_name,
                            'download', d.download,
                            'ping', d.ping,
                            'head', d.head
                        )
                    ) FILTER (WHERE d.id IS NOT NULL),
                    ARRAY[]::json[]
                ) AS "data!: Vec<BmsData>"
            FROM jobs
            LEFT JOIN worker_data as d ON jobs.id = d.job_id
            WHERE jobs.id = $1
            GROUP BY jobs.id
